{"tid":1129813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣5毛] 臺灣杯具 -昨日HONG KONG，今日香港，明日臺灣？","createTime":"2019-04-28T16:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T11:33:09.000Z","uid":89056,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"106cc57ea1ed27c6d39f1d38c34de611096f1a7f","tid":1129813,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/taiwanbeiju/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftaiwanbeiju%2F&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=7c8f511a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/taiwanbeiju/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fz5FDNKt17w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dfz5FDNKt17w&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=8d255978\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fz5FDNKt17w</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ndH5pAKylqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DndH5pAKylqA&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=1b486284\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ndH5pAKylqA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQUMf3rfauM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdQUMf3rfauM&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=913e8780\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQUMf3rfauM</a><br />\n呢幾條video包裝到容易明白香港,英國同中國既歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實極度歪曲事實,參考書籍唔係北京,吉林就係商務而且作者唔係新華社評論員就係親共人士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望連登仔集合力量以正視聽,一齊留言反駁d假訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfor example:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E6%9D%AF%E5%85%B7/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E6%9D%AF%E5%85%B7%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5hong-kong%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A323/741793976001049/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%259D%25AF%25E5%2585%25B7%2F%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%259D%25AF%25E5%2585%25B7%25E6%2598%25A8%25E6%2597%25A5hong-kong%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A323%2F741793976001049%2F&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=f99f79e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E6%9D%AF%E5%85%B7/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E6%9D%AF%E5%85%B7%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5hong-kong%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A323/741793976001049/</a><br />\n<em>不過你以爲故事就這樣畫下完美的句點了嗎？英國可不願這麽乖乖就範說走就走！<br />\n1985年7月1日基本法草委會第一次會議在北京舉行，爲落實一國兩制奠定法制基礎。<br />\n於此同時港英政府不落人後(1985.11)，大發慈悲提出了一套政制改革計劃，决心在香港回歸前「還權於民」，帶領香港走向「民主」！</em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">沈四海@fb 英國在50年代打算退出蘇伊士以東，讓世界各屬地自決或獨立，其中也包括香港在內，數年前英國一批檔案解封，提及五十年代末和中共的接觸，因中共的強硬態度，以至計劃告吹。<br />\n以下這篇報導有詳細交代。網上尚有很多資料。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2014/01/11/60039/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2014%2F01%2F11%2F60039%2F&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=0607c9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2014/01/11/60039/</a><br />\n希望有助在台灣的朋友掃盲。</span>"},{"pid":"d736ef007aad2b20324edd0bf424f98ef043430e","tid":1129813,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T16:26:27.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"1bc2f973fff6e97cede02317d920ec4546fbe034","tid":1129813,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e80e2f2af59aefa3853a7efb3ff2cb2e7027281","tid":1129813,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00dc8819a4d9b2afa51b929a89f2ab572d1a833d","tid":1129813,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"樓主呢啲片點樣搵翻黎?"},{"pid":"34cb55a6a0ab464156ea8c9477e4833069acd099","tid":1129813,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00dc8819a4d9b2afa51b929a89f2ab572d1a833d","tid":1129813,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"樓主呢啲片點樣搵翻黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"YouTube推薦影片見到。"},{"pid":"03a5e63314085462c72bf8e9dfe595a72025a06c","tid":1129813,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a36779bfcd2682b94165544504b3a560985b4e6a","tid":1129813,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:33:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6rIPYeghECM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6rIPYeghECM&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0KyvkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=cfe30847\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6rIPYeghECM</a>"}]}